data.text: Tamara Feldman has: Played Kyla Willowbrook in "Smallville" in 2001. Played Kendra Frank in "Monk" in 2002. Played Courtney Smith in "One Tree Hill" in 2003. Played Anna Sinclair in "Like Family" in 2003. Played Vanessa Cardounel in "Jake 2.0" in 2003. Played Norah Sobel in "Geldersma" in 2004. Played Cassie in "Boston Legal" in 2004. Played Carolyn Williams in "CSI: NY" in 2004. Played Angela Mason in "Supernatural" in 2005. Played Marybeth in "Hatchet" in 2006. Played Bethany in "Perfect Stranger" in 2007. Played herself in "Meeting Victor Crowley" in 2007. Played Poppy Lifton in "Gossip Girl" in 2007. Played herself in "Lucky Shops" in 2007. Played Natalie Kimpton in "Dirty Sexy Money" in 2007. Played Harmony in "Rez Bomb" in 2008. Played Job in "A Woman Called Job" in 2009. Played April in "Royal Pains" in 2009. Played Fiona Crupp in "Drop Dead Diva" in 2009. Played Kamila in "Echelon Conspiracy" in 2009. Played Carroll in "Alyce" in 2011. Played Carrie Raisler in "Switched at Birth" in 2011. Played Ali in "A Blind Eye (Unexpected Views)" in 2011. Played Amanda King in "The Mob Doctor" in 2012. Performed in "Resurrection Slope" in 2013. Played Julia in "Walk the Light" in 2013. Played Job in "A Woman Called Job" in 2013.
